n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Willow Smith|state=autocollapse}}\n\n[[Category:Discographies of American artists]]\n[[Category:Pop music discographies]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox artist discography\n| Artist          = [[Willow Smith]]\n| Image           = Willow Smith.jpg\n| Caption         = Smith in August 2010\n| alt             =\n| Studio          = 3\n| Live            = \n| Compilation     = \n| EP              = 2\n| Singles         = 8\n| Music videos    = 10\n| Option          = \n| Option name     =\n}}\n\nAmerican singer [[Willow Smith]] has released three [[studio album]]s, two [[extended play]]s, eight [[single (music)|singles]] and ten [[music video]]s. In 2010, Smith released her debut single \"[[Whip My Hair]]\", which peaked at number 11 on the US [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]] and at number two on the [[UK Singles Chart]].<ref name=\"Hot100\"/><ref name=\"UKSinglesChart\"/> The song was certified platinum in Australia and the US, gold in Canada and silver in the United Kingdom. Her debut studio album, ''[[Ardipithecus (album)|Ardipithecus]],'' was released on December 11, 2015 through [[Roc Nation]] and peaked on the [[Heatseekers Albums]] chart at number 15.<ref name=\"Ardipithecus\"/><ref name=\"HeatseekersAlbums\"/> She followed with the studio albums ''[[The 1st (album)|The 1st]]'' in October 2017, and ''[[Willow (album)|Willow]]'' in July 2019.<ref name=\"The1st\"/><ref name=\"Willow\"/>\n\n==Studio albums==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of studio albums, with selected chart positions \n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:10em;\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:19em;\" | Album details\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"4\" | Peak chart positions\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Heatseekers Albums|US<br>Heat]]<br/><ref name=\"HeatseekersAlbums\">{{cite magazine|url=http://www.billboard.com/music/willow/chart-history/heatseekers-albums|title=Willow - Chart history (Heatseeker Albums)|accessdate=July 18, 2019|magazine=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Top R&B/Hip-Hop Albums|US<br>R&B<br>/HH]]<br/><ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/willow/chart-history/BLS|title=Willow - Chart history (R&B/Hip-Hop Albums)|accessdate=August 9, 2019|magazine=Billboard}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Top R&B Albums|US<br>R&B]]<br/><ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/willow/chart-history/RAB|title=Willow - Chart history (R&B Albums)|accessdate=August 9, 2019|magazine=Billboard}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Alternative Albums|US<br>Alt.]]<br/><ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/willow/chart-history/alternative-albums|title=Willow - Chart history (Alternative Albums)|accessdate=August 9, 2019|magazine=Billboard}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Ardipithecus (album)|Ardipithecus]]''\n| \n* Released: December 11, 2015<ref name=\"Ardipithecus\">{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/ardipithecus/1440923499|title=ARDIPITHECUS by Willow|work=Apple Music|date=December 11, 2015|accessdate=July 18, 2019}}</ref>\n* Label: [[Roc Nation]]\n* Formats: [[Music download|Digital download]], [[Streaming media|streaming]]\n| 15 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[The 1st (album)|The 1st]]''\n|\n* Released: October 31, 2017<ref name=\"The1st\">{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/the-1st/1440935326|title=The 1st by Willow|work=Apple Music|date=October 31, 2017|accessdate=July 18, 2019}}</ref>\n* Label: Roc Nation\n* Formats: Digital download, streaming\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Willow (album)|Willow]]''\n|\n* Released: July 19, 2019<ref name=\"Willow\">{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/willow/1471582539|title=Willow by Willow|work=Apple Music